have the following values: M (mandatory), O (optional), or C (conditional). A GML application 
schema may be validated by itself. If the 'xsd' and 'gml' arguments are both present, the 
'xsd' value is ignored and the (required) schema reference in the GML instance will be used 
instead.</p>

